(
BAAID NUMBER(32) not null,
"ContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityID" NUMBER(32) not null,

"BrandCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"SeriesCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"IsMasterBrand" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"IsNewBooth" INTEGER default 10 not null,
"BoothStartTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"BoothEndTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
constraint PK_CON_BRANDAREAASSIGN primary key (BAAID)
);
